## Installation

Add `{{ package_name }}` to your `pubspec.yaml`:

```yaml
dependencies:
  {{ package_name }}: ^x.x.x
```

Then run:

```bash
flutter pub get
```

The native libraries will be downloaded automatically during the build process.

